snippet.title: Chicken Police – Into the HIVE! | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you chicken enough to take your investigation into the unsanitary underworld of Clawville?

Chicken Police – Into the HIVE! is the sequel to the critically acclaimed and cluckin’ eggcellent Chicken Police – Paint it RED!. It features a new story, new locations, new characters, and new mysteries to be solved. All are supported by new & improved visuals and a cast familiar to players of the previous game!

Wishlist Chicken Police – Into the HIVE! on Steam: https://bit.ly/3Nnooct

Stay in touch!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ChickenPoliceG
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@chickenpolice
